to a kitchen aide like you?

116
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,760
A Yin, come with me.

117
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,920
You...

118
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,120
What are you doing? What do you want?

119
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,640
No.

120
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,280
Which palace are you from?
You're so handsome.

121
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,240
How come I've never seen you before?

122
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,760
I...

123
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,520
It's an earthquake.

124
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:16,640
Turns out it's a tremor in my heart.

125
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,520
Charming, can't get enough...

126
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,560
Don't.

127
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,680
A spicy boy.

128
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,720
The spicier, the more thrilling.

129
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,280
No.

130
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:34,680
Ladies,

131
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,240
he...

132
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,160
He's my distant cousin.

133
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:42,560
He is a bit off his trolley.

134
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,640
I...

135
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,880
You guys should stop teasing him.

136
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,560
Slow down.

137
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:55,360
What a pity. Didn't expect him
to be a handsome fool.

138
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,280
What are you doing?

139
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,720
Isn't this what you like?

140
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,320
I...

141
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,440
Don't hang around
with those palace maids.

142
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,640
What if they were

143
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,400
