144
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,640
Boys have to protect themselves.

145
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,440
Do you understand?

146
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:28,640
(This palace maid is quite interesting.
I'll tease her a bit.)

147
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,240
What are you going to do?

148
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:44,800
I'll pay attention to what you've said.

149
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,040
But recently,

150
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:51,280
you haven't been cooking
properly for me in time.

151
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:53,800
If I can't eat well,

152
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:55,280
my wound won't heal.

153
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,200
If my wound doesn't heal,

154
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,240
you'll have to keep calling me cousin.

155
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,280
Alright.

156
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,920
I'll cook for you.

157
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:13,480
Oh, in three days, Ms. Jia
and the second young master

158
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,160
will leave the palace
to pray for the City Lord.

159
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:17,120
We all have to go with them.

160
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,560
You must be careful
not to reveal your identity.

